data.title: Golden Globes 2019: the full list of nominees
data.meta_description: Vice, A Star is Born, and The Favourite lead the film nominations. The Assassination of Gianni Versace, Barry, The Kominsky Method, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, and The Americans are all among the television nominees.
data.text: Vice, A Star Is Born, and BlacKkKlansman lead the film nominations, while The Assassination of Gianni Versace is a top TV nominee.
